Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.77,0:22:50.53,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.81,0:22:59.79,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新たな旅立ち 迎えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:10.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失いかけていたsoul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:14.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼び覚ましたconfined
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:24.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共にした日々を 強く握りしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:29.93,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:33.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互いに寄り添い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:38.68,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れことなどない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:44.48,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇が二人わかずとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:53.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かなことが　そう告げているから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.98,0:24:03.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再びで会えるまで　思いよどうか君と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:10.49,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.77,0:22:50.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时 无论何地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.81,0:22:59.79,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接新的征程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:10.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因失去而感到痛苦的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:14.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这禁闭之地 被唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:24.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抓住共同度过的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:29.93,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时 无论何地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:33.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人相互靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:38.68,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无需惧怕任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:44.48,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使黑暗会让两人分离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:53.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为「正确」这样告诉我 直到再会之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.98,0:24:03.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的思念会一直伴于君侧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:10.49,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 我还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到幽灵剧院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经进去了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是咋回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个行李箱突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛西尔老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？你为什么会在箱子里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大危机了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为教师 不能对学生的危机放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是赌上生死的潜入调查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静下来 学生是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思就是 维多利加同学有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加同学 又被父亲叫走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呆在这里 赛西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来不要再靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得和平时的感觉不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…毕竟我是箱子里不是很清…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000008&\fs24\pos(424,367)}在幻影幽灵的指引下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样的暴风雨袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会将你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是 你真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对会找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…维多利加 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压制住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我带路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔伯特·德·布洛瓦侯爵那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊 我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是你的力量为我们所用的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考虑过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么灵异部会现在才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要揭开可可罗斯王妃被杀的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是不是已经有眉目了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有确凿的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要找到那个 抓住犯人的弱点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后得到更高的地位和权势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家里有如此影响力的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才是这个事件的真正犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我心爱的灰狼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可罗斯事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大战开始之前 1914年的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从法国来了位谒见王妃的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下将移送至郊外小屋的王妃迎接回宫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在王妃的房间却发现了无头的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前没有人进出王妃的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了国王陛下一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他并没有带什么可疑的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因就是 几乎与此同时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在王妃的郊外住所中…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目击者中好像也有科学部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后案件就陷入了僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么维多利加想插手这个事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不解决事件的话 那个大概就回不了学园了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是父亲大人的决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 我认为没有什么事件是那个解决不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么担心了 小男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混沌碎片凑齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻报道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料应该是都找齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的情报 维多利加肯定早已知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去收集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要我来收集才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我不把碎片找来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要参与战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和维多利加一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识柯蒂丽亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂丽亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 这个人果然就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加的…母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是16年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个很擅长跳舞的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却突然不知去向了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是她母亲曾生活过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个地方 维多利加她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我记得刚才也有个女孩在看这张照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们长得很像呢 当时我还疑惑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王妃殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么王妃殿下的照片会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩子是尼克尔·露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和可可王妃长得一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都叫她平民区的蓝蔷薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她当时也很受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民区的…蓝蔷薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个开朗的好女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子也不知去向了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 做这行常有这种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 快解开谜团 灰狼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 还缺少混沌碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料都已经找齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰狼不是无所不知的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在碎片都凑齐了的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样无法重组
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招聘秘书？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是1900年的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经是24年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得很清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招聘的条件是金发加上蓝眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连脚的大小都有规定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面试结束之后 就立即离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是些奇怪的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫尼克尔·露露的女演员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在刚才的秘书应征之后就不知去向了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 果然很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再继续调查下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这也是为了维多利加同学嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 平民区的蓝蔷薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的和事件有所关联么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总觉得其中有些联系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概什么时候呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到她做在一辆豪华的马车上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是尼克尔不在登台的10年后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是当上了贵族或是有钱人的情人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 我也这样听说过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在尼克尔失踪10之后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应征秘书 贵族的情人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候买了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得过来一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 还要给苏菲买些礼物才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给苏菲小姐买的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们经常一起来购物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要是知道我一个人来的话 大概会生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲小姐 现在就在苏瓦伦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是来看可可罗斯表演的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是坐她的机车来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？怎么都不叫上我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我交往了10的闺蜜为什么会和久城同学一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往了10的闺蜜？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是在哪里认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌久城同学 所以我不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更讨厌苏菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 可可会不会早些出场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼克尔·露露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说您是她的死忠fans
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 所以当时我很受打击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她的死讯的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你们都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼克尔已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着1900年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是尼克尔小姐失踪的那一年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是招聘秘书的那一年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在10年之后也有人目击到她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请马上住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使做这些事也是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在一旁看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女儿 你的妹妹所隐藏的真正力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人…父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用草药使感官变得敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单调的铃声和摇晃的烛光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些只不过都是为了增强力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么灵异啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是货真价实的科学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有票
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有人巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊 久城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官大概会过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去解开谜团 灰狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仪式结束前 不可以离开这间屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 请在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 久城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰狼 快解开谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人到底是何人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯案手法是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰狼 快告诉偶们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我对着干的势气去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谜团 谜团…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 快住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开灯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 小狼在深处的门里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 维多利加…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 这次的事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不把我卷进来 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我愿意被卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个愿意了解你的一切 愿意走进你的世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有一个这样的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣的仪式被玷污了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快抓住那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 在这里引起骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法从父亲的束缚挣脱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展示力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来解开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会解开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可罗斯事件的谜团由我来解开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为美丽的灰狼母女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献上祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:21:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么想要调查尼克尔·露露
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为可能是能让你开心的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个无聊的秀才挺能干你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表扬你一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.58,0:22:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲的许可下达了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.48,0:22:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去墓地 打开可可罗斯之墓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.93,0:24:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可罗斯的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.74,0:24:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幕帷终于缓缓打开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可 给你的人生装点上鲜花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.07,0:24:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绽放于混沌之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.12,0:24:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为真相的谎言之花
